  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Cost: 2 Creation Points</p><p>Drain: 5 CCD Chakra</p><p></p><p>You modify your creation so that when it explodes it deploys caltrops that cover the ground. </p><p>The ground is covered in a 20-foot radius of caltrops on a point within range. </p><p>The area becomes difficult terrain for the duration. </p><p>When a creature moves into or within the area, it takes 2d4 piercing damage for every 5 feet it travels. </p><p>These caltrops last until the end of your next turn.</p>",
